snippet.title: Chiki's Chase // Launch Trailer - Mobile
snippet.description:
Chiki's Chase is available FREE on mobile: https://www.chikischase.com
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/chikis-chase/id1498398104
Google Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dvdfu.chicken2

The music in this trailer is created by Sean "CosmicGem" Bialo, who also makes the music in the game! https://www.twitter.com/CosmicGemSound

Attributions:
Forest SFX by felix.blume on freesound.org (CC0 License)
Chicken stock footage by Danganhfoto on pixabay.com (Pixabay License)
